description:
Welcome to Antiqo!

We know collecting antiques is fascinating, yet it can also be overwhelming. You discover a rare piece, but you’re not sure of its true value. Your home is filled with vintage finds, but you can’t keep track of their origins. You’re browsing a market and wonder if you’re about to overpay. For many collectors, these challenges can take the joy out of the hunt.

Antiqo was built to solve this. With powerful AI recognition and market insights, Antiqo makes it easy to scan, identify, and organize your antiques, so you can focus on enjoying your collection instead of second-guessing.

SCAN AND IDENTIFY ANTIQUES INSTANTLY

Take a photo of any antique or vintage item and Antiqo will recognize it within seconds. The app identifies key details including object type, style, origin, and era. It works across furniture, jewelry, art, décor, and collectibles, giving you fast, accurate results without the guesswork.

VALUE ESTIMATION & INSIGHTS

Antique values shift depending on rarity, demand, and market trends. Missing this context can mean overspending or underselling. Antiqo helps you stay informed with:

- AI-powered value estimates
- Price history and trend insights
- Comparable items from trusted sources

Whether you’re buying, selling, or simply collecting, you’ll always know where your antiques stand in the market.

ORGANIZE YOUR COLLECTION

Messy notes and endless photos make it hard to keep track of what you own. Antiqo solves this by turning your antiques into a clean digital archive. Save scans, group items by category, mark favorites, and track your collection’s estimated value at a glance.

With Antiqo, everything stays safe, searchable, and easy to update.

AI CHAT FOR COLLECTORS

Antiqo’s built-in AI chat makes collecting simpler. You can ask about an item’s style, cultural background, or historical significance and get straightforward answers. It also helps you discover related antiques and provides context useful for both beginners and experienced collectors.

SUPPORTS ALL TYPES OF ANTIQUES

Antiqo recognizes and tracks a growing range of categories:

- Furniture & décor
- Jewelry & accessories
- Artwork & sculptures
- Coins & collectibles
- Tools & everyday objects
- Rare heirlooms and more

From casual enthusiasts to serious collectors, Antiqo is built for anyone who wants to collect smarter and appreciate history with confidence.

WHY COLLECTORS CHOOSE ANTIQO

- Fast and accurate AI scans
- Value estimation and price insights
- Digital collection management
- Rich historical and cultural context
- Simple, reliable, and built for collectors

Download Antiqo today and uncover the story behind every object. With Antiqo, every scan brings history to life, every antique has its place, and every collector gains confidence to explore the past smarter.

BibleProject is a nonprofit, crowdfunded organization that produces 100% free Bible videos, podcasts, blogs, classes, and educational Bible resources to help make the biblical story accessible to everyone everywhere.
From page one to the final word, we believe the Bible is a unified story that leads to Jesus. This diverse collection of ancient books overflows with wisdom for our modern world. As we let the biblical story speak for itself, we believe the message of Jesus will transform individuals and entire communities.

Many people have misunderstood the Bible as a collection of inspirational quotes or a divine instruction manual dropped from Heaven. Most of us gravitate toward sections we enjoy while avoiding parts that are confusing or even disturbing.

Our Bible resources help people experience the Bible in a way that is approachable, engaging, and transformative. We do this by showcasing the literary art of the Scriptures and tracing biblical themes from beginning to end. Rather than taking the stance of a specific tradition or denomination, we create materials to elevate the Bible for all people and draw our eyes to its unified message.
